676
01:18:23,773 --> 01:18:25,742
Lights out, ten minutes.

677
01:18:54,304 --> 01:18:56,171
Oh!

678
01:18:56,173 --> 01:18:57,672
Shh, shh.

679
01:18:57,674 --> 01:18:59,675
- Get off of me.
- Just relax!

680
01:18:59,677 --> 01:19:00,809
- Leave me!
