692
01:19:50,995 --> 01:19:53,928
Look, I'm puttin'
something together.

693
01:19:53,930 --> 01:19:56,064
This Sunday.

694
01:19:56,066 --> 01:19:58,269
We got room for one more.

695
01:20:00,403 --> 01:20:02,370
